{"tid":1823251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過圍番查飛狗轉頭","createTime":"2020-01-13T13:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T09:48:03.000Z","uid":191650,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2769d2483d05d7d10804f4033d152784ea0f723d","tid":1823251,"uid":191650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"見好多案例巴c單拖俾人圍好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說今日就同幾個fd一齊（5丶6個）<br />\n<br />\n咁就見到橙衫同黑衫<br />\n咁我哋就當住佢面前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾錢入閘<br />\n<br />\n點知有人想查我地<br />\n本身幾個行緊埋黎，可能見我哋幾個比較高大<br />\n<br />\n點知行返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁撚想笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：有fd就唔使驚"},{"pid":"bddde8c7990c43037d227702929916236c3b9f36","tid":1823251,"uid":191650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"搵多幾個一齊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2383d528403406052fc56b836643a5bdf7c96ac2","tid":1823251,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T14:00:20.000Z","msg":"【想贏嘅同我入嚟】<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一人一信逼英國做嘢</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822620</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"14ba6a80e679041fa94a735b9c77951794cd6285","tid":1823251,"uid":191650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T14:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"